dengue module¶

Dengue SEIR Model Class

Contains class for dengue disease model. Inherits from Vector Borne Disease Model class.

Typical usage example:

den = DengueSEIRModel(<config_file_path>)

class dengue.DengueSEIRModel(config_file)¶

Bases: vbdm.VectorBorneDiseaseModel

Models the spread of dengue.

Inherits from the VectorBorneDiseaseModel class. Solves ODE system of equations and plots the resulting curves.

Attributes:

logger: python logging object

model_func(y, t)¶

Defines system of ODEs for dengue model

set_y0()¶

Sets initial states to be passed into model_func
